                    <value>&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #0E0F0E; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Aptos, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#212121&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NL&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Beste relatie,&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Onlangs heeft Aveco u ge&amp;iuml;nformeerd over de MI Retreever peilzender. Een unieke, draadloze oplossing, ontwikkeld door Moving Intelligence en Aveco Verzekeringen, waardoor de Aveco-klant geen aanvullend maandabonnement meer hoeft af te sluiten na aanschaf en u deze zelf kunt installeren als Aveco-partner. Ook wanneer uw bedrijf geen SCM-inbouwerkenning Voertuigbeveiliging heeft. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Aptos, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#212121&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Aptos, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#212121&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NL&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;Wie zijn wij?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #0E0F0E; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Aptos, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#212121&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NL&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;Moving Intelligence is vooraanstaand leverancier van opsporingssystemen voor waardevolle en bijzondere voertuigen, waaronder campers. Inmiddels zijn we al ruim 24 jaar actief en uitgegroeid tot marktleider in Nederland en ver daarbuiten. We zijn premium partner van BMW en Audi en hechten veel waarde aan maatwerk zodat we de klant een optimale ervaring kunnen bieden &amp;eacute;n het gestolen object na diefstal zo snel mogelijk kunnen opsporen.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #0E0F0E; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Aptos, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#212121&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NL&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;In samenwerking met Aveco hebben wij de MI Retreever peilzender ontwikkeld. De Aveco-klant kan, zoals door Aveco in de eerder verzonden e-mail aangegeven, een Moving Intelligence Retreever peilzender aanschaffen voor slechts &lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;euro; 545,-&lt;/strong&gt; inclusief btw, zonder aanvullend maandabonnement en met 5-jarige levensduur! Heeft u het bericht van Aveco niet ontvangen? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.movingintelligence.com/aveco-actie-2024&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Aptos, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#212121&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NL&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;Deze kunt u hier terugzien.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #0E0F0E; margin-bottom: 0px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Aptos, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#212121&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;NL&quot; style=&quot;font-size:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:black&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.2&quot;&gt;Graag maken we binnenkort een afspraak met u om verder kennis te maken en om u te informeren over de MI Retreever peilzender. Heeft u nu al vragen? Neem contact op met accountmanagers Rob van den Bogaert of Paul Schuttevaer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
